<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-PMU_B03.html">PMU_B03</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>An event B03 signals to delete the record with the healthcare administration information about an individual healthcare practitioner to correct erroneous entries.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The EVN segment is used to indicate the effective or planned date.</p>
</div>
